1
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,280
Little Boss

2
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,920
We're in your territory now.

3
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,359
Don't run off again.

4
00:01:40,519 --> 00:01:41,359
Do you hear me?

5
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,640
Go to your dad.

6
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:47,560
Go back now.

7
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,040
Assemble the troops. Prepare for battle.

8
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:57,640
Yes, sir.

9
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,640
What is it now?

10
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,439
This battle is unavoidable.

11
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,400
Wasn't everything settled?

12
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:05,480
If we don't have to fight, let's not fight.

13
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,920
As a commander,

14
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,480
leading subordinates onto the battlefield,

15
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,840
how can one leave the outcome to chance?

16
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:11,920
You helped me save my son,

17
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,120
and secured my territory.

18
00:02:13,519 --> 00:02:15,560
But Division Commander Chen won't let this go.

19
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:16,639
Trust me.

20
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,520
Division Commander Chen

21
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:19,280
is also ready.

22
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,439
Commander Liao's position is on low ground.

23
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:23,199
Fan's troops are likely here.

24
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:25,159
You circle around from across the river.

25
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:26,560
I'll flank from this side.

26
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:29,120
We'll form a pincer movement.

27
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,479
There shouldn't be a problem.

28
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,080
Don't worry.

29
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,560
The things I promised you,

30
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,919
you won't be shorted a single one.

31
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,159
You can rest assured too.

32
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:38,560
My army will give its all.

33
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,680
You lot,

34
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:45,400
go prepare as well.

35
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,680
Yes, sir.

36
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,879
Commander.

37
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:56,439
Then what do I need to do?

38
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,960
You don't need to be involved.

39
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,800
I'll listen to your arrangements, Commander.

40
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,400
Then I'll stay at base camp,

41
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,960
prepare good wine and meat,

42
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,560
and await your triumphant return.

43
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,240
From now on,

44
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,719
you don't need to be involved in anything.

45
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,120
Commander, Commander.

46
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,599
Did I do something wrong?

47
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,520
Although today,

48
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,000
Silly Fan ruined my plans,

49
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,240
I still admire him.

50
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,360
He has courage and strategy.

51
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,840
He values loyalty and righteousness.

52
00:03:31,199 --> 00:03:32,759
He is what a soldier should be.

53
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,719
But you?

54
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,759
You've read so many books in vain.

55
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,680
You're full of wicked schemes.

56
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,400
Above, you do not respect heaven and earth.

57
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,759
Below, you have no pity for the people.

58
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:46,680
No fear in your heart, no restraint in your words or deeds.

59
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,080
You don't deserve to wear this uniform.

60
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,479
Men!

61
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:50,319
Here!

62
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,520
Drag him out.

63
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:53,159
Strip him of his uniform.

64
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,400
Commander! Commander! Commander!

65
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,719
I can change!

66
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,039
Whatever the problem is, I can change!

67
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:58,840
Change?

68
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,319
If I keep you around,

69
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,199
I'll be the laughingstock of others.

70
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,280
From now on,

71
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,800
you're on your own.

72
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,599
Take him out.

73
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,080
Move!

74
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,000
Commander, I was wrong! Commander!

75
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,599
Move!

76
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,759
Commander, give me one more chance!

77
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:14,120
Commander! Commander! Commander!

78
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,720
Fine.

79
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,959
Fine.

80
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,600
This isn't over.

81
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,120
This isn't over.

82
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,360
Commander Liao

83
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,920
Congratulations, congratulations

84
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,040
You tricked me, saying you'd find the Lucky General

85
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,720
You disappeared for so long

86
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,480
Where is the Lucky General?

87
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,879
This is him

88
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,720
Division Commander

89
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,319
I came specifically to ask for...

90
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:08,800
...that reward of one hundred silver dollars

91
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,920
How many times are you going to sell me?

92
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,160
Whose side are you on, you bastard?

93
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,680
I'm on your side

94
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,920
Commander, you and our Brigade Commander...

95
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,959
...are truly destined to meet by fate

96
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,279
Reward him

97
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,519
Thank you, Commander

98
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,399
Brigade Commander

99
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,120
I've brought the troops outside

100
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:28,720
Just give the order...

101
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,759
...and we'll immediately submit to Commander Liao

102
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,279
Who said I was going to submit?

103
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,279
I'm leaving

104
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,120
Where are you going?

105
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,639
Where *can* you go?

106
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,079
Chen and Wei already view you as a rebel army

107
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:46,000
They won't let you off

108
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,480
With your current military strength...

109
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,879
...you definitely can't beat them

110
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,959
Why not stay and fight with me?

111
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,759
Thank you for thinking highly of me, Commander Liao

112
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,839
I don't want to fight anymore

113
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,120
The guts of you Division Commanders...

114
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,439
...are really twisted

115
00:05:58,759 --> 00:06:00,800
Calculating back and forth all day long

116
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,480
I can't out-calculate you

117
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:06,000
My goal this time was just to save my little brother

118
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,600
Now that I've handed him over to you...

119
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,759
...my mission is complete

120
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:11,879
Are you really leaving?

121
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,279
Think it over carefully

122
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,279
I've thought it over

123
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,240
Good

124
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,800
Everyone has their own aspirations

125
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,680
Since you've already decided...

126
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:27,959
...I won't force you

127
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,639
Thank you for your help this time

128
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,639
I believe...

129
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,680
...we will meet again very soon

130
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,439
Farewell

131
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,120
Stop

132
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,079
Where are you going?

133
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,560
I'm following Big Brother Fan

134
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,439
To save you this time...

135
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,439
...I almost sacrificed many lives

136
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,759
If you keep messing around like this...

137
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:52,519
...you'll get your Big Brother Fan killed too

138
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,680
You didn't save me

139
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:55,240
Big Brother Fan saved me

140
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,319
This is the last time I'm saving you

141
00:06:59,000 --> 00:06:59,959
There won't be a next time

142
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,079
Think about it

143
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,240
Little Boss

144
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,720
Go back

145
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,439
You must remember...

146
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,600
...I will always be your big brother

147
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,199
On this matter...

148
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,839
...you must listen to our Old man

149
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,399
Take care

150
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,319
Where are we heading?

151
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:43,279
First, let's leave this place of trouble

152
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,040
Brigade Commander, have you considered...

153
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,079
...that Commander Liao is actually...

154
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:48,720
...someone worth following?

155
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:52,319
I also feel we're birds of a feather

156
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,759
I've followed two Division Commanders already

157
00:07:56,199 --> 00:07:57,600
And I've learned quite a bit

158
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,040
We can strike out on our own...

159
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:01,120
...and give it a try ourselves

160
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:03,199
I didn't expect you to have such ambition

161
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:05,800
You all say I'm a Lucky General

162
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:09,319
This time, I'll be a Lucky General for myself

163
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:22,399
Damn it!

164
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,839
Call out to them!

165
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,439
Damn it!

166
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,399
Commander Wei

167
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:33,560
We're not here to fight

168
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:38,120
We're going back home

169
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,720
What's going on?

170
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,159
Brigade Commander Fan

171
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,639
What are you doing here?

172
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,759
Our Commander said...

173
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,919
...we would meet again very soon

174
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,960
It happened too fast

175
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:13,559
He wants me to thank you properly

176
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,919
Then we have no choice but to fight

177
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,960
Fine, let's fight together

178
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,000
Alright

179
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:33,879
Here.

180
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:37,159
Have some figs from my hometown, Weiyuan.

181
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,960
Here, share them among the brothers.

182
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,159
Here, Number Two.

183
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,120
Number Four.

184
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,159
This Division Commander Chen...

185
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,960
stays holed up in the city all day.

186
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,240
Commander Wei fires two shots today,

187
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,159
and fires two shells tomorrow.

188
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:55,080
It's been so long.

189
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,000
Brother, when will this battle end?

190
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,639
I've been sick of fighting for a long time.

191
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,200
Then what are we doing here?

192
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,639
Then let's inspect...

193
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,720
how you guys have been fighting lately,

194
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,320
see if there's any improvement.

195
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,399
In war,

196
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:12,440
you can't be afraid of death.

197
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,320
If a bullet is meant to hit you,

198
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,960
it'll hit you even if you burrow underground.

199
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,840
If a bullet isn't meant to hit you,

200
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,240
even if you stand here like a telephone pole,

201
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,879
it won't hit you.

202
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:25,440
Do you understand?

203
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,240
And then there's the machine gun.

204
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,440
What should you do?

205
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,480
Get down!

206
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,360
Idiots.

207
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:38,039
That's a machine gun spraying aimlessly.

208
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:39,559
You should run.

209
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:42,039
But if the machine gun...

210
00:10:44,399 --> 00:10:45,240
what should you do?

211
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,159
We run!

212
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,039
Idiots.

213
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:50,720
That's a machine gun firing aimed shots.

214
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:52,559
You should get down.

215
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,279
And another thing.

216
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:58,240
Why are you in the trenches,

217
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:00,360
while I stay in a shell crater?

218
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:01,639
Why?

219
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:02,559
Because...

220
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,799
Because... no second shell...

221
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,159
ever lands in the same crater.

222
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,320
For example, this shell...

223
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:13,600
Run!

224
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,639
Run!

225
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:20,919
Are you okay?

226
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,480
Is everyone okay?

227
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,919
Brother, are you okay?

228
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,360
Brigade Commander Fan,

229
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,159
didn't you say a second shell...

230
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:30,279
wouldn't land in the same crater?

231
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,200
This...

232
00:11:34,639 --> 00:11:37,000
is the second lesson I'm teaching you.

233
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:39,679
Nothing in this world is absolute.

234
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:44,120
Food's here! Food's here!

235
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,399
What are we eating?

236
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:49,799
Yuxiang shredded pork, stir-fried liver,

237
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,480
and steamed pork belly.

238
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:53,600
And your favorite, twice-cooked pork.

239
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,559
Brigade Commander Fan!

240
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:05,799
The twice-cooked pork... is it still there?

241
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:06,840
Twice-cooked pork...

242
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:16,240
Screw the food.

243
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,919
Beiping and Tianjin have been occupied.

244
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,120
Songhu is also in a stalemate.

245
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,519
Fighting has started in Taiyuan too.

246
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,480
The main Nationalist forces have been deployed.

247
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:02,759
It's a struggle.

248
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:09,759
Constant bombing, the people are suffering.

249
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:13,360
Times are hard.

250
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:17,480
I also want to ignore what's happening outside.

251
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:19,200
But speaking from my conscience,

252
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:20,639
I can't do it.

253
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:24,399
I just don't know if General Liu can stay out of it.

254
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:28,879
When the nest falls, no egg is safe.

255
00:13:31,679 --> 00:13:32,679
Let me ask you something.

256
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:36,039
If the two of us rashly send troops,

257
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,720
would it be against the rules?

258
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,639
Doing as we please,

259
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:46,159
acting first and reporting later...

260
00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:49,679
haven't we done enough of that?

261
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,240
Exactly.

262
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:53,360
I've lost my patience long ago.

263
00:13:53,559 --> 00:13:55,279
I was just waiting for you to say that.

264
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,639
Let me tell you,

265
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,320
under our command,

266
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:00,879
those few mischievous brats...

267
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,679
normally,

268
00:14:02,679 --> 00:14:05,039
we'd let their petty squabbles slide.

269
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:05,559
Yes.

270
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,600
But today is different from the past.

271
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,679
We might still...

272
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,360
need to go straighten them out.

273
00:14:11,559 --> 00:14:12,200
It's very necessary.

274
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,840
What the hell are we fighting for?

275
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,960
Well said.

276
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,519
Our compatriots

277
00:15:22,039 --> 00:15:24,240
are in deep suffering.

278
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:26,559
Following the Northeast,

279
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,080
now it is North China.

280
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:31,279
The Japanese imperialist bandits

281
00:15:31,559 --> 00:15:33,120
intend to turn the Chinese people

282
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,960
into a nation of slaves.

283
00:15:36,519 --> 00:15:37,600
Facing a formidable enemy,

284
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,159
we can no longer fight amongst ourselves.

285
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,000
We must all unite

286
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,399
and face the external enemy together.

287
00:15:44,799 --> 00:15:46,120
Save our compatriots,

288
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,720
defend our homeland,

289
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,799
and drive the Japanese aggressors

290
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:51,559
out of Chinese territory.

291
00:15:52,279 --> 00:15:53,799
I answer the call.

292
00:15:55,159 --> 00:15:56,399
Here we are,

293
00:15:56,799 --> 00:15:58,600
fighting back and forth,

294
00:15:59,399 --> 00:16:01,960
just to seize a town or occupy a village.

295
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,879
The Japanese

296
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,759
want to destroy our nation.

297
00:16:07,679 --> 00:16:08,720
I answer the call.

298
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,159
The Japanese aggressors are bastards.

299
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,600
If one comes, I'll shoot one.

300
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:16,399
If two come, I'll cut down a pair.

301
00:16:18,919 --> 00:16:19,759
Division Commander Chen,

302
00:16:20,679 --> 00:16:21,960
in the face of national righteousness,

303
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,120
we must put aside our grievances.

304
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,240
Commander Liao,

305
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:28,240
you just focus on winning battles.

306
00:16:29,279 --> 00:16:31,159
When you return from driving out the Japanese aggressors,

307
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,879
our score

308
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:35,159
can be settled then.

309
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:36,440
Good.

310
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,159
Well said.

311
00:16:39,399 --> 00:16:40,759
From now on,

312
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:43,159
we Sons of Sichuan

313
00:16:43,519 --> 00:16:46,440
united as one, forging the Sichuan Army together.

314
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:48,279
United against the enemy,

315
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,360
ready at any moment

316
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,679
to march out for the country.

317
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:54,639
Kill!

318
00:16:54,919 --> 00:17:00,919
Kill! Kill! Kill!

319
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,879
Now,

320
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:05,320
the special envoy from headquarters will announce orders.

321
00:17:05,720 --> 00:17:07,039
By order of General Liu:

322
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:11,640
Fan's unit is united, righteous, brave, and decisive,

323
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:13,039
and highly praised.

324
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:17,240
Fan's unit is hereby incorporated into the 36th Brigade,

325
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:20,559
and the 36th Brigade is expanded into

326
00:17:20,799 --> 00:17:22,960
the 3rd Division of the 21st Army.

327
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:27,200
Fan Pengju is appointed Major General, Division Commander.

328
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:39,200
Attention!

329
00:17:43,039 --> 00:17:44,759
Come, let me toast everyone.

330
00:17:45,079 --> 00:17:47,440
Congratulations to Big Brother and Scar on becoming Regimental Commanders.

331
00:17:48,039 --> 00:17:49,960
Congratulations to Laoyao on becoming Battalion Commander.

332
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:51,759
Congratulations to Lao Er, Lao San, and Lao Si

333
00:17:51,759 --> 00:17:52,920
On becoming Platoon Leaders.

334
00:17:53,039 --> 00:17:54,279
Come, come, come.

335
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:56,160
Drink up! Cheers!

336
00:17:56,839 --> 00:17:58,160
I want to join your troops.

337
00:17:58,599 --> 00:17:59,839
And go with you.

338
00:18:01,279 --> 00:18:03,160
We are going to fight the Japanese bandits.

339
00:18:03,559 --> 00:18:06,240
Bullets don't have eyes on the battlefield.

340
00:18:07,079 --> 00:18:08,400
I am also a Son of Sichuan.

341
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,200
You are all going to fight.

342
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:12,359
I can't be a coward hiding in his shell.

343
00:18:12,599 --> 00:18:13,720
I am a Descendant of generals.

344
00:18:14,119 --> 00:18:15,400
I should set an example even more.

345
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:18,920
I don't care.

346
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,599
I'm going with you no matter what.

347
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,160
You want to go?

348
00:18:22,599 --> 00:18:24,519
Then you should go with your Old man.

349
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:25,759
He can't control me.

350
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,839
I'm not important to him anyway.

351
00:18:27,920 --> 00:18:29,039
What do you mean not important?

352
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,839
Didn't he save you in the end?

353
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,759
One moment he saves me, the next he doesn't.

354
00:18:33,039 --> 00:18:34,440
He might as well not save me at all.

355
00:18:35,039 --> 00:18:37,200
It's made my feelings very complicated.

356
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:41,359
As a Division Commander...

357
00:18:43,359 --> 00:18:46,880
He has so many soldiers who need to follow and respect him.

358
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:49,759
Sometimes he has no choice.

359
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:53,720
You have to understand.

360
00:18:54,359 --> 00:18:57,160
You'll understand once you're on the battlefield.

361
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,640
So you agree to let me go with you?

362
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,680
The nation is in crisis.

363
00:19:02,319 --> 00:19:05,400
We men should have some guts.

364
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,319
But I have three conditions for you.

365
00:19:08,839 --> 00:19:09,680
First.

366
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:12,039
No unauthorized actions.

367
00:19:12,319 --> 00:19:13,079
Second.

368
00:19:13,279 --> 00:19:15,240
Do not leave my sight on the battlefield.

369
00:19:15,359 --> 00:19:16,200
Third.

370
00:19:17,359 --> 00:19:19,359
Go back and make up with your Old man.

371
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:23,240
I agree to the first two right now.

372
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:24,960
As for the last one...

373
00:19:25,759 --> 00:19:27,200
Let me think about it first.

374
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:28,680
Alright.

375
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,680
Before we set out...

376
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,240
Think it over.

377
00:19:33,599 --> 00:19:34,880
Yes sir, Division Commander!

378
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:39,559
Brothers!

379
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:41,279
Our ambition...

380
00:19:41,279 --> 00:19:44,079
Has always been to roam the world and uphold justice.

381
00:19:44,799 --> 00:19:45,759
From now on...

382
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,279
I'm going to show what I'm truly capable of.

383
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,480
Brothers...

384
00:19:50,160 --> 00:19:52,960
We don't ask to be born on the same day...

385
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:55,599
But we ask to die on the same day.

386
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:57,200
Us lot...

387
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,759
If we end up dying on the battlefield...

388
00:20:00,039 --> 00:20:01,319
Then we are true brothers.

389
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,880
Don't jinx it!

390
00:20:03,119 --> 00:20:04,960
We haven't even left and you're talking about death.

391
00:20:05,119 --> 00:20:06,279
Why can't we...

392
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:07,400
All come back alive?

393
00:20:09,599 --> 00:20:10,519
Exactly.

394
00:20:11,119 --> 00:20:12,559
I haven't even taken a wife yet.

395
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,240
When I get back...

396
00:20:14,559 --> 00:20:16,319
I'm definitely going to sleep with a woman in my arms.

397
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,240
I think...

398
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:19,640
As long as us brothers are together...

399
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,680
I'm not afraid.

400
00:20:20,799 --> 00:20:21,559
Worst case scenario...

401
00:20:21,559 --> 00:20:23,279
In the next life, I'll still be a hero.

402
00:20:24,799 --> 00:20:27,000
Anyway, following Division Commander Fan...

403
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,440
We're real men.

404
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,920
Rise up!

405
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,839
Come, come.

406
00:20:30,839 --> 00:20:32,440
A toast to Big Brother.

407
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:33,839
Cheers!

408
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,079
Cheers!

409
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,400
Pockmarked Tiger.

410
00:20:49,559 --> 00:20:51,079
I haven't come to see you in a long time.

411
00:20:52,079 --> 00:20:53,160
Did you miss me?

412
00:20:54,839 --> 00:20:55,880
I missed you.

413
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:04,599
Those Japanese aggressors...

414
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,880
Are even worse than that guy named Wei.

415
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:09,319
I'm going to go deal with them.

416
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:12,039
Once I've dealt with them...

417
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,240
I'll come back to keep you company.

418
00:21:15,279 --> 00:21:16,839
I'll still be your loyal servant.

419
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,279
If I don't come back...

420
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:01,359
One, two, one!

421
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,880
One, two, one!

422
00:22:03,079 --> 00:22:05,839
One, two, one, halt!

423
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,799
Turn left and right!

424
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,839
The Young Master is back! The Young Master is back!

425
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:13,640
Young Master, let me.

426
00:22:13,759 --> 00:22:14,640
I'll do it myself.

427
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:15,960
Close the door.

428
00:22:36,599 --> 00:22:37,480
Old Master

429
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,480
The Young Master is back

430
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:41,720
Please open the door and take a look

431
00:22:43,599 --> 00:22:45,880
Old Master, come out and take a look

432
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:46,880
I won't shout anymore

433
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:32,079
I'm not back to stay

434
00:23:33,119 --> 00:23:35,880
I came back this time mainly to say goodbye to you...

435
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:37,720
...and to the ancestors

436
00:23:38,799 --> 00:23:41,319
Once I leave, I don't know...

437
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:16,440
You were right to make me study

438
00:24:18,039 --> 00:24:20,759
You were right to spank me too

439
00:24:21,759 --> 00:24:23,039
Even burying me alive...

440
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:24,680
...was all correct

441
00:24:27,079 --> 00:24:28,400
Only now do I realize...

442
00:24:29,119 --> 00:24:30,440
...you did it all for my own good

443
00:24:33,759 --> 00:24:36,160
The lampwick cakes you love...

444
00:24:37,599 --> 00:24:38,799
I promised...

445
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:40,920
...that as soon as I had money...

446
00:24:41,279 --> 00:24:42,920
...I'd buy you enough to eat your fill

447
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:46,240
The leaf tobacco you love to smoke...

448
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:48,519
...I've brought it back for you this time

449
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:51,039
Top-quality Shifang tobacco

450
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:56,039
Fan Pengju has been unfilial

451
00:25:05,079 --> 00:25:06,000
Just now...

452
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:09,400
...I asked the ancestors to bless Granduncle

453
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,440
To wait safe and sound for my return

454
00:25:14,319 --> 00:25:15,960
I also prayed for Yu Zhen

455
00:25:16,799 --> 00:25:18,359
I've been looking for her all this time

456
00:25:19,559 --> 00:25:22,319
There's no time to find her now

457
00:25:25,079 --> 00:25:26,279
Counting the time...

458
00:25:28,039 --> 00:25:29,359
...my child...

459
00:25:33,599 --> 00:25:34,960
...should be one year old

460
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:38,519
I haven't even given him a name yet

461
00:25:40,039 --> 00:25:41,559
I must trouble you, Granduncle...

462
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:44,079
...to help your great-grandson...

463
00:25:44,519 --> 00:25:47,160
...choose a resounding name

464
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:49,759
Raise him to become...

465
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:53,279
...the kind of person you hope for

466
00:26:00,119 --> 00:26:01,480
I'm leaving

467
00:26:36,119 --> 00:26:37,079
Your old man...

468
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,519
...is off to do great things

469
00:26:40,599 --> 00:26:42,039
Let him leave with some swagger

470
00:26:43,799 --> 00:26:45,240
Don't let him be weighed down by worry

471
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,640
I entrust my son to you

472
00:27:26,079 --> 00:27:27,039
Young Master

473
00:27:27,759 --> 00:27:28,640
Young Master

474
00:27:29,079 --> 00:27:29,920
What are you doing here?

475
00:27:30,039 --> 00:27:31,640
The Old Master told me to go with you...

476
00:27:31,759 --> 00:27:32,759
...to take care of you

477
00:27:33,359 --> 00:27:34,400
Get in line at the back

478
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:50,720
The vast rivers and mountains are now shattered

479
00:27:51,559 --> 00:27:55,400
The iron hooves of the Japanese bandits ring out

480
00:27:56,039 --> 00:27:59,240
Sacrificing oneself for loyalty is like filial piety

481
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:02,799
Fighting bravely on the battlefield makes a national hero

482
00:28:03,279 --> 00:28:07,759
In this national crisis, we leave Sichuan to fight

483
00:28:08,319 --> 00:28:12,599
If we win, we return in triumph

484
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:18,000
If we do not win, we return wrapped in shrouds

485
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:23,160
We fight for our fathers, brothers, wives, and children

486
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:29,480
No return to Sichuan without victory!

487
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:39,599
No return to Sichuan without victory!

488
00:29:15,519 --> 00:29:19,799
Sichuan will not fail the nation!

489
00:29:20,039 --> 00:29:57,519
Sichuan will not fail the nation!

490
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:54,839
Men at their birth are naturally good

491
00:30:56,119 --> 00:31:03,240
Their natures are similar, their habits become different

492
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,440
Baby...

493
00:31:06,279 --> 00:31:08,839
Don't be as silly as your old man
